with this and say,

00:13:13.930 --> 00:13:17.060
OK, there's a feeling of relief.

00:13:17.060 --> 00:13:19.120
There's a feeling of
relief, believe it or not,

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:21.650
of like, OK, I'm not dead.

00:13:21.650 --> 00:13:24.890
I'm not inside there, and my
children are not inside there.

00:13:24.890 --> 00:13:29.060
There's a feeling of guilt,
the guilt being around,

00:13:29.060 --> 00:13:32.580
maybe I didn't do enough when
I could have done enough.

00:13:32.580 --> 00:13:35.110
Maybe I just took
things for granted.

00:13:35.110 --> 00:13:38.790
And I settled into this
domesticated life of,

00:13:38.790 --> 00:13:41.970
I have mine, so you know what?

00:13:41.970 --> 00:13:44.860
I don't got to worry about them.

00:13:44.860 --> 00:13:46.690
And all these other
different emotions

00:13:46.690 --> 00:13:49.750
are happening at the same
