00:14:31.530 --> 00:14:33.990
than our demographic?

00:14:33.990 --> 00:14:39.270
Would the police have gone in
quicker if there was different

00:14:39.270 --> 00:14:44.870
folks, if it was a church
rather than a temple?

00:14:44.870 --> 00:14:48.350
And that really eats at you.

00:14:48.350 --> 00:14:52.820
And I think like, that's been
the part, for me and Arno,

00:14:52.820 --> 00:14:55.880
that's been our inspiration,
that's to say, you know what?

00:14:55.880 --> 00:15:00.190
Forgiveness is going to
look a lot like vengeance.

00:15:00.190 --> 00:15:02.320
And we're going to
be vengeful and say

00:15:02.320 --> 00:15:04.360
that nobody is
going to ever have

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:09.484
to have this feeling of not
being worth enough to save.

00:15:09.484 --> 00:15:11.900
