00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:22.120
on the back with the sword.

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:25.190
I didn't know anything
about what Sikh was about,

00:16:25.190 --> 00:16:29.630
but I did know that
because of who Sikhs were,

00:16:29.630 --> 00:16:33.080
because they were so
visibly different than even

00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:35.150
other people of
color in the states,

00:16:35.150 --> 00:16:39.080
I just had this
sinking feeling that I

00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:44.510
had something to do with
this, that my old ideology had

00:16:44.510 --> 00:16:45.680
something to do with this.

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:48.830
There was white supremacy
involved in one way or another

00:16:48.830 --> 00:16:53.420
and very possibly directly
motivating the shooter.

00:16:53.420 --> 00:16:58.580
So from my client's
office, and by the way,

00:16:58.580 --> 00:17:00.079
this client is
still a good friend

00:17:00.079 --> 00:17:02.120
and aware that I was doing
this on billable time,

00:17:02.120 --> 00:17:08.310
but I recorded a video
response to the shooting,

00:17:08.310 --> 00:17:12.599
and really, just first of
all, said how devastated.

00:17:12.599 --> 00:17:18.050
I was to imagine people who
have lost their fathers,

00:17:18.050 --> 00:17:19.920
three boys lost their mom.

00:17:19.920 --> 00:17:24.050
Like there's a grandpa
there who was killed,

00:17:24.050 --> 00:17:27.480
and really feeling
that kind of suffering.

00:17:27.480 --> 00:17:29.240
I wanted to convey
that in the video,

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:33.200
how dedicated I was to bearing
witness to the suffering

00:17:33.200 --> 00:17:36.960
and also to burying as
much of it as I could.

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:40.760
And then, I went on about how,
when things like this happen,

00:17:40.760 --> 00:17:45.330
we really have to let
compassion be our vengeance.

00:17:45.330 --> 00:17:47.930
We have to let
what's most beautiful

00:17:47.930 --> 00:17:51.440
about our human experience
come to the rescue

00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:52.560
of this situation.

00:17:52.560 --> 00:17:56.030
And I went on a bit
about how we really

00:17:56.030 --> 00:17:58.130
got to see ourselves
in each other,

00:17:58.130 --> 00:18:01.430
no matter what, if we're
Democrats and Republicans,

00:18:01.430 --> 00:18:04.550
or if we're black and white,
or we're rich and poor,

00:18:04.550 --> 00:18:05.180
like whatever.

00:18:05.180 --> 00:18:08.030
We still got to see that
we're all human beings first

00:18:08.030 --> 00:18:09.710
and foremost.

00:18:09.710 --> 00:18:14.540
And then, I went home and just
glued myself to the media,

00:18:14.540 --> 00:18:17.326
and by the end of
the night, it was

00:18:17.326 --> 00:18:19.325
revealed that the shooter
was a white supremist,

00:18:19.325 --> 00:18:21.230
an affiliated white supremist.

00:18:21.230 --> 00:18:24.920
They didn't say his
