00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:40.730
His name was Wade Michael Page.

00:18:40.730 --> 00:18:42.426
They announced his background.

00:18:42.426 --> 00:18:45.410
He was from Colorado
originally, then

00:18:45.410 --> 00:18:49.130
North Carolina, and
only recently Milwaukee.

00:18:49.130 --> 00:18:51.900
Even though so much of my time
back in the hate group days

00:18:51.900 --> 00:18:55.270
was literally
hazed by alcohol, I

00:18:55.270 --> 00:18:58.100
might have met
this guy in person.

00:18:58.100 --> 00:19:01.850
They later revealed that he got
radicalized while in the United

00:19:01.850 --> 00:19:05.120
States Army, and came
out of the Army in 1998

00:19:05.120 --> 00:19:07.490
a full-blown white
power skinhead.

00:19:07.490 --> 00:19:09.860
I was able to rule
that out also,

00:19:09.860 --> 00:19:12.170
that I didn't know
this guy personally.

00:19:12.170 --> 00:19:17.420
But it didn't really change the
urgency that I felt to respond

00:19:17.420 --> 00:19:19.310
and the responsibility
that I felt

00:19:19.310 --> 00:19:24.290
to help transform this
atrocity into something that

00:19:24.290 --> 00:19:28.420
would actively counter hate and
violence from that day forward.

00:19:28.420 --> 00:19:31.170
SPEAKER 1: So now, you too
are very good friends now.

00:19:31.170 --> 00:19:35.940
But I would love to hear how you
decided to meet the first time.

00:19:35.940 --> 00:19:37.680
What were the
expectations going in,

00:19:37.680 --> 00:19:39.712
