meeting the first time,

00:19:39.712 --> 00:19:41.670
coming from such different
backgrounds and such

00:19:41.670 --> 00:19:44.420
a unique connection
between the two of you?

00:19:44.420 --> 00:19:46.300
PARDEEP KALEKA: Yeah.

00:19:46.300 --> 00:19:50.220
So after the shooting happened--

00:19:50.220 --> 00:19:51.900
my dad was temple
president and he

00:19:51.900 --> 00:19:56.190
was president for 15 years,
which is a long time according

00:19:56.190 --> 00:19:58.290
to Sikh Indian politics.

00:19:58.290 --> 00:20:02.540
The president of any church,
synagogue, mosque, like Google

00:20:02.540 --> 00:20:03.510
aura, right?

00:20:03.510 --> 00:20:06.540
So I mean, his
dream was basically

00:20:06.540 --> 00:20:10.920
to make a sanctuary where
people, Sikhs, could come to.

00:20:10.920 --> 00:20:13.800
And within that time, he did.

00:20:13.800 --> 00:20:16.810
He fulfilled what
