00:29:18.910 --> 00:29:20.310
Just keep testing it.

00:29:20.310 --> 00:29:21.460
Be courageous.

00:29:21.460 --> 00:29:22.230
Be courageous.

00:29:22.230 --> 00:29:24.390
The thing that you
