00:29:24.390 --> 00:29:26.250
is what you should be doing.

00:29:26.250 --> 00:29:28.500
Try to say yes more
than you say no.

00:29:28.500 --> 00:29:30.840
Obviously there are things
that you want to say no to,

00:29:30.840 --> 00:29:32.710
but be courageous.

00:29:32.710 --> 00:29:36.330
And so just keep going in
that sort of intention,

00:29:36.330 --> 00:29:38.640
that spirit of
being courageous, we

00:29:38.640 --> 00:29:42.980
find ourselves at this
restaurant together.

00:29:42.980 --> 00:29:46.210
And the first time
that I saw him,

00:29:46.210 --> 00:29:49.580
I was like, what am I going
